name: smudged dots | black and white
description:
This purse is machine-sewn and assembled with care.
It's a handy size that will hold all your cash(notes), credit cards and coins!

Size: Approx. 4" wide x 4 1/4" deep 
Outside material: cotton
Lining fabric: cotton

All stress points are reinforced with double-stitches for maximum strength.
No two purses are identical and there may slight inconsistencies in similar items.

'Imperfections' are the beauty of hand-made products.
